{"tid":675860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將中國踢出環太軍演     王毅：非常沒有建設性","createTime":"2018-05-24T01:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T12:54:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0a0f7b6443f2f31863c8ec12a35b416ecff72f","tid":675860,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T01:44:51.000Z","msg":"在美國的國務委員兼外長王毅說，美國取消邀請中國參加環太平洋軍事演習的決定輕率。<br />\n<br />\n王毅與美國國務卿蓬佩奧在華府會談後兩人共同會見記者。王毅說，美方的做法非常不具建設性，也是輕率的決定，無助中美互相了解。<br />\n<br />\n在朝鮮半島問題上，王毅表示，如果美國要與北韓和平共處，現正是美國總統特朗普與北韓領袖金正恩舉行峰會的時候。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1397848-20180524.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1397848-20180524.htm&d=h5CBWGnPckCkRoAY9OKbor%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f0488718\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1397848-20180524.htm&h=d9a7b1e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1397848-20180524.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4581f4d455bd3a714b6e83ed01766e80eb0e5d8b","tid":675860,"uid":47355,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T01:47:41.000Z","msg":"唔使去軍演，可以用少d油洗少d錢，又贏"},{"pid":"756aceb9e79738294558f94b89d4301456dfda46","tid":675860,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T01:49:56.000Z","msg":"嬴國可保持軍事秒密，又嬴"},{"pid":"5b30b8cc059c1d9e938aa6565d2f3a8f3ae15e96","tid":675860,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:01:32.000Z","msg":"自己搞個一帶一路軍演，搵啲巴基斯坦人一齊玩，又贏"},{"pid":"aecb89cec1a06e9ab79252631f7e802fc6b8163f","tid":675860,"uid":47259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:13:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王毅說，美方的做法非常不具建設性，也是輕率的決定，<span style=\"color: red;\">無助中<del>美互相了解</del>方偷野</span>。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal